    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab incarnationis
                        eius millesimo centesimo sexagesimo quarto, sexto idus aprelis, indictione
                        duodecima. Manifesti sumus nos <persName><name ref="Wilielmus"
                                >Guilielmus</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Borgognone"
                                >Borgongnone</name></persName> germani quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Herimanni">Armanni</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Talia">Talia</name></persName> relicta quondam suprascripti
                        Armanni et filia quondam <persName><name ref="Albertus"
                            >Alberti</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Avenante"
                                >Avenante</name></persName> uxor suprascripti Borgongnoni et filia
                                <persName><name ref="Gheroinus">Geruini</name></persName>, quia ego
                        qui supra Talia mihi consentiente suprascripti germani filii et mundualdi
                        mei in cuius mundio ego esse visa sum, et ego qui supra Avenante mihi
                        consentiente suprascripto viro meo ubi interfuit notitia <persName
                            key="#Judge"><name ref="Lotteringus">Lutteringi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> domni imperatoris, (…) nos insimul per han
                        cartulam vendimus et tradimus tibi <persName><name ref="Montanus"
                                >Montanino</name></persName>, divino nomine dei gratia rectori <rs
                            key="#Hospitals">ospitalis</rs> Dei et <orgName key="#Hospitals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3206">Sancti Gilii et Sancti Iacobi</orgName> de
                            <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207">Altepascio</placeName>,
                        ad opus et utilitatem predicti ospitali idest unam petia de terra nostra que
                        est campus in <placeName ref="#places/3229">Campo de Piscia et
                            Vinnarese</placeName>, in loco et finibus ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/3229">Selva Salese</placeName>. Et tene uno capo in
                            <placeName ref="#places/3233">Togiano</placeName> et alio capo in Selva
                        Salese, latus unum in terra de filii quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Sigismundus">Sesmondini</name></persName> et alio lato in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Maginectus">Mainecti</name></persName> quondam
                        suprascripti Armanni. (…) <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: sol. duocentum
                        quadraginta bonorum denariorum. (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum (…)
                        et insuper penam argenti optimi libras triginta. (…) Actum loco et finibus
                        de <placeName ref="#places/3211" key="#Churches">Vivinaria</placeName>,
                        intus <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2089" key="#Churches">Sancti
                            Salvatori</orgName>. (…) Singnus manus <persName><name ref="Hughicio"
                                >Ugicioni</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Gherardus"
                                >Gerardi</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Accattapane"
                                >Acattapani</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Wilielmus">Guilielmi</name></persName> rogatorum testium. (S)
                        Ego Lotteringus domni imperatoris Federigi iudex interfui et hic subscripsi.
                        (S) <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Glandulfus"
                            >Glandulfus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni regis post traditam complevi et dedi. </ab>
                </div>
